  question:
    "Jai Sri Ram\n\n"+
    "What is the best way to wash out bad karma in these kaliyug? Is it possible in this mechanical world and all negative people around you! what is the best way to purify soul and negative attitude in a person in present hectic world?\n\n"+
    "M. ARVIND. Rao.",
  answer:
    "Divine Soul,\n\n"+
    "Negativity around you doesn't matter once you realize that the world begins with you. There is no reality without an observer and observer is you. The negativity will stop affecting once you realize your soul. The storm in the ocean which you see all around does not matter once you hold on to the anchor i.e. your soul.\n\n"+
    "To realize the soul there are two ways-- (1) Knowledge i.e. the Supreme Knowledge (2) Devotion.\n\n"+
    "Choose the path which suits you. If you are kind of a person who likes to question things, then go for the supreme knowledge. If you are kind of a person who indulges in emotions rather than questions, go for devotion.\n\n"+
    "Blessings"
