    header: "A MIRACLE...AND A PRAYER REQUEST.",
    question: "\"Continued from #49819 ,\n\nJai Sri Ram and my heart felt obeisance to all those who serve Him and Sri Anjaneya.This May 2015 when I went to my home after the incident happened with the second person who's name is Vijay Srinivasan,when I had written about being cheated,my father gave me something of Hanumanji and told me that Lord Hanuman will fulfill your desire.This person was in my mind and his family members like me very much so his father had asked me to get sweets for him.I returned to my work place after one month.Just before joining I had to go to his house to give sweets to his father but I did not inform him as he had rejected me.\n\nBefore going,the previous day I wanted to know whether lord Hanuman is with me and whether the thing which my father gave me was by the Lord's will or not ,I asked Lord Hanuman to show me a miracle when I go to their house the next day.I was worried that I did not inform him and was meeting his parents what may happen.Everything went smooth,he behaved well,just when I was about to leave his house A small monkey from no where came and sat in their doorway...everyone was shocked because they have been living in that house for so many years and never such a thing happened.\n\nEven Vijay repeatedly was asking me how was it possible,I knew what happened but just kept silent.It was a miracle.Thanks to my Lord Sri Ram And His devotee Lord Hanuman.After some days Vijay once again sent me the proposal for marriage which was also a miracle.\n\nBut after few days of accepting he rejected me again.He is like a child ,due to his past karmas he lacks understanding and decision making ability also he is not physically not well,But he is a nice person.The astrologers have told.Astrologers have also predicted that he will come back to me. There was no communication for more than a month but the day the astrologer predicted, the very next day he messaged me telling me if marriage did not work out should I not ask him.That was the third miracle.\n\nI cannot change him its only God who can perform miracles.All the above are impossible miracles for me.So I have a prayer request kindly pray for this person so that he will understand me and accept me,I do not have any selfish motive to marry him ,its just that he and his family are very pious people and I want to serve them and take care of them as my parents and his parents have arranged this marriage.All will be blessed by this marriage."
