    question: "Hi.. I want to know does every soul gets Moksha?? How many lives does one soul have before it gets dissolved completely or gets Moksha ??\n\nIs there any way I can know About my previous birth?\n\nI 've always been love starving since birth and don't find to peace anywhere. I have been cheated in love. I was a non believer in God because I could not find any answers for my suffering. One day something unusual happened. There was a Lord Hanuman photo in the gym i used to go.. I was feeling very be that day feeling helpless and tears in my eyes.. when I looked up suddenly I saw Lord Hanuman's pic and felt something inside. Like someone gave me the strength . I have never been the same after that. I became devotee of Lord Hanuman. It has given me strength to move forward. I still struggle with my problems and wants to know some answers. Sometimes I feel all this could be related to my previous lives deeds .. please reply!\n\nJai SriRam!! Jai Hanuman!!",
