    header: "MY EXPRRIENCE AND QUERIES",
    question: "Lord Hanuman please forgive me for my sins.\nI am resident of India and i have experienced lord many times. Recently I completed my education and was searching for a job. I applied in almost 100 cmpanies but got no rply. One day during my daily prayers I told lord krishna that I want to work, I want to do something and within 3 4 days I got job. I want to thank god for listening my prayer.\n\nI have many queries, but the first one comes to my mind is that why God has choosen India as a place to take birth, why not any other land, and what about the dinasours and other thing, lord hanuman doesn't say anything about them?",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nThere are two ways to explore this universe -- inward way, outward way.\n\nWestern people follow outward way. They keep searching things in the outside world which is a maze. They search for planets, they experiment on animals, they make observations and devise theories from those observations.\n\nOn the other hand eastern people explore inward. They go towards the root of everything which is the supreme reality.\n\nThat is why western people are still confused while eastern people found the truth of universe long long ago.\n\nThey are lost in dinosaurs while our sages speak to God.\n\nBlessings"
