    id: 1078,
    header: "MY FATHER'S LIFE",
    question: "dear Setuu,\ni am a 22 year old, just finished my graduation and started working in a software company. i am very much concerned about my family and especially my father who is 54 year old. My father is from a middle class family and from his birth he has been suffering a lot in his life in terms of both health as well as wealth. He has really tried very hard to keep up our family. He is a very kind hearted person and has been helping so many people and he is a very great devotee of God and keeps trust in God always. But he is already midway in his life and he is still not settled in his life. he is right now facing financial problems. i am trying to help my family the best but my contribution is not enough for my family to run smoothly. i dont know what has to be done. My father also gets frequent health issues and 2 months back he had a fracture in his leg when he met with an accident. He was unable to come out of that problem and he faced problem with his leg for nearly 3 months even though the doctor said it was a minor one. Then in the last chapter i prayed lord hanuman to cure his health problems and keep him healthy for rest of his life. then the miracle happened. one day suddenly when i called my father and enquired about his leg he said he slowly started loosing pain and its getting better. i really feel lord hanuman is listening to my prayers.\n\nBut my sincere prayer to lord anjaneya is i want my father to live happily for his rest of his life as he has undergone so much of difficulty from his birth till now. i pray the almighty lord hanuman to solve the financial problem my father and my family is facing right now and give my father health and wealth for rest of his life.\n\nAnd my special request to Setuu is i want to know from the mathangs why my father is facing so many problems in life and what is the way to get out of these frequent troubles he is facing.\n\nI hope lord anjaneya will protect my father and family and will answer my prayers as he did the last time which was a magic.\n\ni thank lord hanuman for solving health issues of my father and pray that he also solves his financial problems.",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nYour father is very much attached to his family. He indulges himself in every small thing of the house. Lord Hanuman gave him a very slight bump (problem) in order to lower his indulgence in family issues but the reverse happened. He became more and more attached to family matters. He is a great soul. Had he not indulged into every small thing of this world, his soul had the capability to move towards Moksha. But now that you have expressed your wish that you want him only to be happy in current human life not Moksha, we have conveyed this to Lord Hanuman. His troubles should start vanishing from today. You should lower your attachment and see him as a great soul which has acquired a human body to settle some Karma accounts. Do not tell anything to him about what we have told you here. Just lower attachment from your side.\n\nBlessings"
