    question: "Jai Shree Ram\nJai Hanuman\n\nYou know everything Hanumanji. The scenario at my parental house is not so good and friendly. Right now no one but we live there. Not everyone but some of my uncles are in favour of selling this parental house. They don't want to live here. According to them, if they live here, they will not prosper. The place is not good. Some say there are some spirits or ghosts or something like that. So, they are in favour of selling this and shifting to some other place. But we haven't experienced anything like that with God's grace. I don't know whether there is any spirits or ghosts or anything like that. Is it really so?\n\nSometimes, they even tell us not to live here. I am jobless right now and looking for a good job. They tell me not to live in this house. If I live in this house, I won't get a good job and I will not prosper in life. Is it really so?\n\nPrabhu you know everything. We are not in a position to leave this house and move to some other place. We don't have money to buy a new flat or new house right now. We have to live here only. Moreover, I don't want to move to some other place. I want to live here only whenever I come home in holidays or festivals.\n\nHanumanji, bless me and my parents and make everything alright so that we may live in this house only with peace. Please forgive us if we have done any mistakes knowingly or unknowingly either in this birth or in previous births. Even if there is any spirits or ghosts or anything like that in our house, let it not harm me or my parents. Protect us against all odds. Keep your blessings on me and my parents always Prabhu.\n\nI know karma of my parents, my uncles, my relatives and mine are different and I am not mixing it. I am just requesting you to make everything alright. It's just between you and me prabhu.\n\nMy sincere pranam to Mathangs and Setuu Masters.\n\nThank you Mathangs. Thank you Setuu.\n\nRegards.",
