    header: "MY PROBLEMS",
    question: "Skip to main content\nMY PROBLEMS\n\nThe Experience/Query posted below was posted by a devotee/Sadhaka.\n\nWill my problems ever be solved ?I mean the legal troubles.When will I be free from Life's bondage?\n\nSetu Speaks:\n\nDivine Soul,\n\nYour troubles will be over and when they are over you will realize why they were created. It will take some time. These circumstances will make you like banks of a river. The banks of river always remain still while gallons of water flows through them. Same way, you will realize that you are a soul which is untouchable by any trouble. All the trouble is just flowing via body and mind. Then you will attain supreme bliss. Then you will realize that your troubles were boon in disguise.\n\nBlessings\n\nImmortal Talks",
