    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nKnowledge is the only way. If you have read Lord's Leelas so far sincerely, you would know that two things are separate- (1) Soul (2) Body+Mind. You need to recognize these two things separately. Because of the disturbances of the world, your body and mind may not support you in your efforts to remain connected with the Lord. Hence leave them aside. Let your body and mind deal with the world but separate your soul from body+mind. Awaken your soul and let it remain connected with the Lord while body+mind struggle with situations of the world. Do not try to connect your body+mind to Lord. Just connect your soul, everything else shall fall in place by itself.\n\nBlessings"
