    question: "My koti koti pranam at the lotus feet of Bajrangbali, i wanted to know from the lord is that i often remain in bad health since my childhood and after several doctors visit and hospitals across India the problem never ends completely and doctor tells this is psychological. Mayi know the reason behind it and when i will be cured completely.\n\nI want my every action/free will/wishes/desires whatever be , governed/directed by my lord, is there any way my prabhu can help me out?",
