    id: 1192,
    header: "AS A NOR HUMAN BEING HOW TO STOP ASURRAHS TO DO EVIL ACT?",
    question: "Opportunity to experience evil is what all Asurrahs always look in to.\nIf the desire to have the gemstone (fulfill our wish) is here, then the gemstone (fulfillment of wish) are also here.\nIf a desire is expressed here, it will get fulfilled without any hurdle of conflicts. If we want to fulfill our desire, we need to express only just that – without any emotions and other desire attached to it.\nThe nature of Asurrahs, once they see that a soul is not allowing them to do evil act, they move on to explore opportunities elsewhere.\nWith every bad karma fruit getting dropped in to red basket we will feel our soul get lightened as it was getting rid of influence of Asurrahs.\nSince we have grown up in special circumstances hence we lose purity of soul and our karmas have been largely influenced by Surrahs and Asurrahs. We need more opportunities of making arpanam.\nI should know how to handle such a situation and save our loved one from going deep into evil which, even yesterday, I missed in case of my son, when by mistake he hit food plate by leg and I lost my cool to a large extent. I will try to Control self-first.\nSince other members are not internally strong to fight with invisible bad power, being a normal human being how I (my soul) can stop and not to allow Asurrahs to do evil act so that they (Asurrahs) move on to explore opportunities elsewhere?\nPl Guide!!!!",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nYou should not react with anger. Asurrahs initially capture only the body-mind. You can evoke intellect and Samskara of your child immediately to stop the Asurrahs from capturing them. If you react with anger, that means you are making the Asurrah influence you also. Do not react with anger. Try to evoke intellect and Samskara of your child.\n\nBlessings"
