    question: "My humble Pranams to Hanuman ji,Im very thankful to every other soul helping to heal the wounds in life. I have never been so lucky in life, neither peace nor happiness lasts for a moment in my life my only source of peace is Lord. Incidents in life shook me so much that sometimes I feel there is no value for dharma. Im confused about what is truth? whom to believe? Why do I fear of losing my loved one? Afterall I'm a human being don't I deserve a ordinary life with a peaceful family, or am I expecting so much from you Lord that I cannot be provided? When I seek the feet of Almighty i feel safe and happy but I feel insecured when i finish off my prayers, Why do I experience such things? Please help me out Lord ! Jai Shri Ram ! Jai Hanuman !",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nSuppose you are going out for a long drive. You have no destination. You are just going for fun wherever the road leads you. What would be your motivation to return home?\n\n(1) If the sun sets, you will think about security and would like to turn back towards home.\n\n(2) If you see something unpleasant on the road e.g. an accident, your mood will get spoiled and you would like to turn back.\n\n(3) If you get bored of driving for long time, you will turn back.\n\nSame is the case of soul. It takes up many bodies in mortal worlds but ultimately it has to head back home i.e. VishnuLoka. It has to get Mukti or Moksha from birth cycle. What is the motivation required to a soul to head back home?\n\n(1) When a body starts getting old, then the soul realizes the futility of life. It turns towards God. However it is too late when the realization happens in old age. In old age, the soul does not have enough options to settle its Karma accounts. Therefore it just takes another body and same thing repeats again. In youth the body doesn't let the soul realize truth and then in old age it is too late.\n\n(2) When a body sees something unpleasant in the world, it is forced to think about the higher reality and thus the obstruction of the body from the soul gets removed.\n\n(3) When a bored explores all the luxury the materialistic world offers, it gets bored of it. Then it rises to the level of soul and starts exploring the higher reality,\n\nYou and majority of souls fall in category 2. You are lucky that you are heading home, divine soul.\n\nBlessings"
