    question: "hi This is Chaitanya.i just read your article,that LORD HANUMA just visited.i personally feel that i am very interested in spirituality.i am having lot of doubts but for now i will query a thing..you said that, Lord HANUMA came back and he will come again after 41 years.\nfirst of tell me at the time of lord RAMA ruling BHARATHA KANDA...what about remaining people who are living not in india.in some puranas it was stated that india is called jambhudveepa and like wise lot of places are having among one ketumala(presently name gutamela in mexico).\nso at the time of lord rama ruling what about the people living in ketumala..did they know about lord rama that he is an avator of vishnu,all these things..\nAt the time of lord rama living itself did the people knows that he is GREAT LORD or after his PASSOUT.\n\nPLEASE FORGIVE ME IF I SPOKE ANY THING WRONGLY BUT AT ANY COST REPLY ME.I WANT TO KNOW A LOT PLEASE\n\nregards",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nQueries from an innocent heart can never be wrong. We always welcome sincere questions.\n\nThere are two ways to know something- (1) To know from mind (2) To know from soul. Mind has its limits. It can know about something if it experiences something with 5 senses. A soul can know about anything in the field of consciousness and even beyond!\n\nIf your question is about knowing from mind, then NO, not everyone knew about Ram when He was living on earth. If your question is about knowing from the soul, yes, every enlightened soul knew Ram.\n\nKnowing from mind used to happen through wanderers. People used to wander from one place to another and used to tell stories about divinity of Lord Ram and thus He became popular. That is why when He came to jungles for Vanvas, jungle people knew about Him. But stories can travel only where people can travel. If there was no communication between two pieces of land separated by oceans, then Lord Ram's stories could not travel. So it is quite possible that people of some piece of land did not know about Ram.\n\nOn the other hand knowing from the soul is possible only if a person or living being lives at the level of soul and not at the level of body and mind. Even the birds knew about Ram because their souls were connected to the supreme soul which governs the whole universe."
