    question: "Jai Shree Ram\nJai Hanuman\n\nFirst of all, accept my sincere pranam.\n\nI have a query regarding the arrival of Lord Hanuman in Mathang Community.\n\nIt is mentioned that Lord Hanuman comes to Mathangs every 41 years and stays with them like a guest. Recently he visited them in 2014. He creates certain situations in their daily lives in order to clear blockages of their minds and souls so that they can realize God and attain Moksha. The head of the Mathangs(Baba Mathang) notes down every word and every act of Lord Hanuman in a log book. This log book serves as a guide for new members of their family for next 41 years.\n\nIt is also mentioned that apart from this log book, they also chant a secret Mantra in their daily worship. When they chant this Mantra, Lord Hanuman appears before them and they can speak to him to clear their doubts.\n\nNow, my query is when the Mathangs can talk to Lord Hanuman whenever they want using the secret Mantra, then, how can it be said that Lord Hanuman comes to Mathanga Community every 41 years?\n\nIs it like that Lord Hanuman comes to live with them as a guest every 41 years? And when they chant the secret Mantra Lord Hanuman comes before them and clears their doubt and again disappers? One more thing does Lord Hanuman come in their daily Shakshat Hanuman Pooja?\n\nPlease forgive me if I asked anything wrong. I have been following your website for more than a year but I don't know why these queries came to my mind today only.\n\nThank you Setuu.\nThank you Mathangs.\nRegards.",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nLord Hanuman physically lived with Lord Ram in Ramayana period. After that Lord Ram departed from the mortal world but Lord Hanuman and other devotees of Lord Shri Ram can still have Darshan of Lord Shri Ram.\n\nSimilarly Lord Hanuman comes to physically live with Mathangs every 41 years but they can have His Darshan anytime they want.\n\nBlessings"
