    question: "Jai Shree Ram\nJai Hanumanji\n\nI have received two lines of the secret Mantra to call Hanumanji. There are total 36 lines. The first line I received through mail. In the mail, it was mentioned that I can chant the Mantra anytime anywhere if I know its meaning. After sometime I got the second line.\nEarlier in my profile, two conditions were mentioned regarding the Mantra. Condition 1 was to make Lord Hanuman my Guru, which I have already fulfilled and Condition 2 was regarding some distance that no one should be around that area in whose heart Lord Hanuman doesn't live. Now, how should I fulfill Condition 2?\nPlease tell me how should I chant these two lines of the Mantra? Are there any specific conditions or rules to be followed to chant the Mantra? Please tell me the actual process or procedure to be followed to chant the two lines of the Mantra.\nThanks and regards.\n\nJai Shree Ram\nJai Bajrangbali",
