    question: "Dear Setuu friends and Matangs,\nFew days back, in trans I show a horse like creature....it wasn't dream....I was sleeping, suddenly I became awake...saw a horse like creature in the upper part of my wife and after sometime....there was no horse and again saw my wife standing. ...again I am saying. ...it wasn't a dream....please let me understand the significance and meaning of what I saw.\nFew months back I saw Lord Shiva in trans even though I wasn't praying to Lord Shiva but prayed to Lord Hanuman.\nPlease help\nPlease convey my sincere prayers to Lord Hanuman.\nRegards\nTamoghna Dassharma",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nIt wasn't a dream. These experiences are for imparting supreme knowledge. But you need to ponder over them. You need to compare these two version of yourself :\n\n(1) When you are in this so called reality\n(2) When you are in the so called trans\n\nIn both these states, you have a body and the respective outer things. For example right now, you have a body and the computer or mobile in front of you. If you go into trans, then you will have a body and something else around you.\n\nSo in these two states, you have two different bodies. That means, your body is not a static thing. You are changing your body every moment. Every moment you have a new body. Only your soul remains same. Everything else is changing every moment. An ordinary human being cannot figure out this illusion but you are going through an important phase in your life. This phase can either lead you to enlightenment or you will again come back to living as an ordinary human being trapped in illusion of Maya.\n\nBlessings"
