    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nSuppose there is an ocean and there are many deep divers. They all go into the ocean and dive deep into its bottom. They come out with different different things. They all describe their deep diving experiences in various ways.\n\nSome will say- \"There are many jewels deep in there.\"\n\nOthers will say- \"There are green creatures in there.\"\n\nOthers will say- \"There are stones in there.\"\n\nDescription of the experience will vary but experience is same.\n\nThat explains many religions and philosophies. Descriptions are different, experience is same.\n\n-----\n\nPhysical things have no relation with God and God's prayer. Restrictions only create different vibrations.\n\nFor example, you can open a place and fix a rule that only women will be allowed. No men will be allowed. That place will have a unique vibration.\n\nVibrations affect mind. Prayer is done with soul not with mind. For peace of mind, some people go to resort others go to \"so called temple\". Temple is just a place with different vibrations.\n\nPrayer is done with soul not with body or mind. But mind should be calm in order to elevate at the level of soul. It depends on you what you do to make your mind peaceful. If you need \"temple vibrations\", go to a \"temple\". If you need \"resort vibrations\", go to a resort. Or stay at home and quiet your mind with meditation.\n\nCutting nails, periods, non-veg all these things happen at physical level. It has no relation with prayer. If you are non-veg but you can elevate yourself to the level of soul, you are eligible for prayer of God. However you should respect the restrictions of a place. If there is a place which restricts non-veg people, that is to create a different vibration. Don't take offense. Go to another place which allows non-veg people or just stay at home and connect to God.\n----\n\nYour prayer shall be fulfilled. Take care of these three things-\n(1) Make sure you have a deep desire to reach goals.\n(2) Make sufficient efforts required to fulfill that desire otherwise your soul will just go to Swapan Lok and fulfill those deep desires. It will never become reality here in this world.\n(3) In order to get help of Lord Hanuman in removing obstacles, never allow demons of \"fear\" and \"worry\" etc make room in your heart and mind. If these demons remain there, you will not get help of Lord Hanuman. You have to dedicate your entire heart-mind space to Lord Hanuman.\n(4) Keep your prayer simple. Just ask, \"O Lord, fulfill my wishes.\" Do not bring your family, society and world into your wish. Otherwise their Karma will also affect you. Just keep it between you and Lord. Nobody else. Everyone related to you will automatically get fruits when your wish gets fulfilled.\n\nBlessings"
