    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nString donation takes place under the supervision of Gods. Usually a loved one's strings are used or that of an ascetic for whom everyone is loved one. Only Gods can facilitate the transfer of strings of time.\n\nDecision in life should be taken as per Dharma. Do you have a Dharma set for yourself? A set of principles on which you live life? The problem is that, in Kaliyuga most of people are infected with Asurrahs. When somebody gives advice, you cannot figure out whether the advice has been contaminated by an Asurrah or is it pure. Therefore trust Dharma. When you pray or meditate, for some moments you rise at the level of soul. At that time your mind produces Asurrah free thoughts. At that time you can trust your mind and make decisions.\n\nBlessings"
