    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nThere is no fixed date for release of chapter. It usually takes 28 days but it may take upto 90 days also. Your extreme attachment to your mother's soul is causing obstruction to her new birth. Give up your attachments and let Lord Hanuman take care of her soul. He knows what is good for a soul and what is not. She was your mother only in this birth. In her previous births, she was mother of so many souls. Had they got too much attached to her, would you get a chance to become her son? Open your eyes of knowledge and recognize your soul. The 10 chapters which have been published so far can break hardest of attachments. It seems you have not read these chapters sincerely. Read and meditate on the knowledge. In the first chapter itself you can realize that relationships are nothing but an illusion. If you are unable to break attachment, turn it into absolute love. When you experience absolute love about your mother, you shall be able to see her in every particle of this universe. That will help your soul in moving towards Moksha.\n\nBlessings"
