    question: "During my childhood days my parents used to worship Lord venkateshwara, then they swithced to Shiridi Sai babad and now they are devotees of lord krishna (ISKCON).They used to press their devotional preferences on me but. Ritght from my childhood from the moment i heard stories about Hanuman. I started loving Hanuman, I dont know why am not interested in any other gods though my parents say that Lord krishna Is the Supreme Lord of all. I Love Only Hanuman ji, I dont know why.Every thing about hanuman motivates me.When ever i look at hanuman's pictures i have some strange Un explainable feeling. I want to know why am interested only in Lord hanuman.?\n\nPlease help me to find answer for this.",
    answer: "Divine Soul,\n\nIn Kaliyuga, only the sages can communicate with Lord Vishnu/Krishna directly in two-way communication. For a householder, it is not possible to establish direct soul connection with Krishna. Even if you are a devotee of Krishna, He directs Lord Hanuman to help you because being immortal on earth, Hanuman has access to both the world of Gods and world of human beings. Whether you devote yourself to Krishna or Hanuman, Hanuman will help you because Lord Hanuman is here in mortal world only on the directions of Lord Vishnu. Till Vishnu takes His last Avatar, Hanuman will help the devotees.\n\nBlessings"
